OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy overnight, with sporadic
OL,7,Fbursts of rain moving eastwards for
OL,8,Fmuch of the evening. Perhaps turning
OL,9,Fdrier during the second half of the
OL,10,Fnight, with a few breaks in the cloud
OL,11,Facross the east possible.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FBreezier through Tuesday,
OL,14,Fwith best of cloud breaks and sunshine
OL,15,Facross eastern areas. Remaining damp
OL,16,Fwith possible rain over the Pennines,
OL,17,Fthis might become more persistent and
OL,18,Fheavier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
