OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday, early rain clearing, then
OL,7,Fcolder, brighter with blustery
OL,8,Fshowers. Thursday, windy with showers,
OL,9,Fperhaps more persistent rain. Friday
OL,10,Fless windy with sunshine and showers.
OL,11,FTemperatures near normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
